{"tid":769652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【玩撚完系列】外匯","createTime":"2018-08-06T10:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T11:39:22.000Z","uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2eae626b98b31c6a927f4ec9cb72c6d0684513dc","tid":769652,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T10:47:28.000Z","msg":"香港其實已經係玩撚完<br />\n就好似依家個個港豬都知有粒隕石撞緊落黎地球咁。只係大家都唔知幾時撞到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢粒隕石就係共產黨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n共產黨係由一班只為當前利益既人組成既一個黨。<br />\n共產黨依家有幾亂，有幾唔掂，心水清既人好清楚<br />\n因為打緊貿易戰/貨幣戰既關係，所以共產黨依家好等美元用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而黨內既美元唔頂得好耐，因為佢之前已經不停咁印銀紙。至於個關係我唔係呢到解釋太多。<br />\n依家全黨內仲有好多美金既地方就係-香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講左咁耐，戲肉黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開頭都講到明，玩撚完。自自然然就係冇解決方法架啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問既係，如果你係共產黨，你會用咩方法拎走香港既外匯儲備（美金）？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68005fcdb0cacce80a3a90e26925d28a20b4f723","tid":769652,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de09b98e5a15bb603fc49dc1b7955f66336935c7","tid":769652,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"太難明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44496167cdcae96c03a352e7d14eb6a439d0604c","tid":769652,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"毒L開po冇人理"}]}